## Step 3: Deploy to Vercel (The Easy Part!)

1. Go to **vercel.com** in a new tab

2. Click **"Sign Up"** (top right)

3. Select **"Sign up with GitHub"**

4. Authorize Vercel to connect to your GitHub

5. After signing in, click **"New Project"** (top right)

6. You'll see your repos listed. Click **"Select"** next to your `Mental-Health-Pregnant-women` repo

7. Vercel will auto-detect it's a React app (shows framework detection)

8. **Just click "Deploy"** button (don't change any settings)

9. **Wait 30-60 seconds** while it builds... You'll see a progress bar

10. When done, you'll see:
```
✓ Preview Ready
your-project-url.vercel.app
```

🎉 **That's your live dashboard URL!**

